title: THE ILLEGITIMATES 01 (of 06) (2013) (IDW) (digital-Empire) JAMES
description:
THE ILLEGITIMATES #1 (OF 6)

Publisher: IDW

(Writers) Taran Killam, Marc Andreyko
(Artist) Kevin Sharpe

Jack Steele: World renowned agent of OLYMPUS, super-spy, debonair, lover of ladies, man-slut.

While facing off with his arch-nemesis, Viktor Dannikor, Steele faces his biggest defeat, but who will take his place? Olympus scrambles to find not one, but FIVE newbie agents to fill the void and, unbeknownst to them, they share a common thread. Can these five strangers embrace their fates and come together to save the world? They are THE ILLEGITIMATES! And if you called them bastards.... you'd be absolutely right!

From actor/comedian Taran Killam (SNL, The Heat, 12 Years a Slave), Eisner and Harvey nominated writer Marc Andreyko (Torso, Manhunter, Captain America & Bucky), and artist Kevin Sharpe (Avengers, Legion of Super-Heroes) comes an exciting and high-adventure series that will change your views on super-spies forever!

In Shops: 12/18/2013
$3.99
